description:
Create src/components/tick-toast-stack.ts for toast notifications:

@customElement('tick-toast-stack')
export class TickToastStack extends LitElement {
  @state() toasts: Toast[] = [];
}

interface Toast {
  id: string;
  message: string;
  variant: 'primary' | 'success' | 'warning' | 'danger';
  duration?: number;
}

Features using sl-alert:
- Stack multiple toasts in bottom-right corner
- Auto-dismiss after duration (default 5s)
- Manual dismiss via close button
- Variants: success (green), warning (yellow), danger (red), primary (blue)
- Animate in/out smoothly

Global API:
- window.showToast({ message, variant, duration })
- Or emit 'show-toast' event that tick-board handles

Test: Trigger multiple toasts, verify stacking and auto-dismiss
